#Parcel 

-- Dev Build
--Local Server
--HMR=Hot Module Replacement
--File Watching Algorithm --written in c++
--Caching --Faster Builds
--Image Optimizations
--Minification
--Bundling
--Compressing
--Consistent Hashing 
--Differential Bundling (Your app can be opened in old version of Internet explorer , CHROME (tO SUPPORT THE OLDER  Browsers))
-- Diagnostic
--Error Handling
-- Also give way to host on https as well
--Tree Shaking(will remove the unused code for you)
-- Different dev and prod bundles 

To ocreate the prod build

npx parcel build index.html

dist (developent) -- when you execute parcel it generated the development build

